high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table then take a step to your left then walk to the wall to the right of the fridge then turn right.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you to the left of a mug.
Turn right and take three steps forward then turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Go back to where you got the spatula.
Put the spatula horizontally under the two mugs.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the round table, move to the left of the table, then turn right to face it.
Pick up the spatula from the round table.
Turn right and move forward, then turn right and cross the room to go to the sink.
Clean the spatula in the sink.
Turn right to go to the counter, then turn right to return to the round table.
Put the spatula on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the round table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the table.
Pick up the spatula from the table.
Turn right and go forward. Turn right again and head to the sink.
Place the spatula in the sink. Wash the spatula then take it out.
Turn around to the right and go back to the table.
Put the spatula back on the table.
